name: TAHAAN

briefDescription: Since 2016, Tahaan is actively working in areas of water conservation and providing clean drinking water. We work in villages as well as cities to plan the water resources and increase green cover.OUR AIM IS TO MAKE THE SOCIETY AWARE WHY WATER IS THE ELIXIR AND WHY SMART USE AND COLLECTION OF IT WILL BE BENEFICIAL FOR A PERSON IN THE LONG RUN.
